Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with predicting trajectories from RGB camera inputs. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper deals with predicting trajectories of road-agents. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is likely as the paper uses a deep learning-based instance segmentation algorithm and an LSTM-CNN neural network architecture for trajectory prediction. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is likely as the paper deals with developing an algorithm for predicting future trajectories. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is unlikely as the paper does not deal with cryptography or security.
